Nurses are the #UnseenAthletes of healthcare. 💪🩺

During a typical 12 hour shift, you probably walk thousands of steps. 👣 

Fill in the blank: “During a 12 hour shift, the amount of steps I usually walk feels like _________.”

Tell us in the comments below and tag a friend for a chance to win a carefully curated gift box with products from @therabody @bombas @careandwear @wearkizik @spongellebeyondcleansing plus a spa voucher to help your body recover from the physical demands of a shift.

One lucky winner will be announced on 5/13 at 10 am ET via an update to this post and DM from this account, connectRN’s official Instagram page. Good luck!⁣ 🎉
